    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Sealed beasts' fortitude becomes your own. While gaining the benefits of your Twisted Chakra Cloak, you can further alter your form to imitate the true form of your Sealed Beast, growing armor, scales, or even a shell. As a Bonus Action you can spend 10 Twisted Chakra, increasing your Twisted Hit Points and Maximum Twisted Hit Points by 30 times the Twisted Chakra Cloak Stage you are benefiting from. This effect doesn't stack.</p>",
